{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_06_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚 3話 思い返すと恥ずかしい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月スト新曲のジャケット撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of new song's cover photoshoot for Moon Tempest",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n撮影の立ち会い、来てくれたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san.\nYou came to oversee the shooting‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遅くなってごめん。撮影は順調？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for being late. Is the shoot going well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……それが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　なんだか琴乃達がこっちを\nじろじろ見ているような……気のせいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? It feels like Kotono and the others are\nstaring at us or something. Is it just my imagination?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "この前撮影してもらった雑誌の見本が\nさっき事務所に届いたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sample of the magazine we shot for\nlast time just arrived at the office‚ and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私と手を繋いでるのが{user}さんだって\nすぐにバレちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was immediately got caught that you were the one\nholding hands with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺、手しか写ってないのに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even only our hands were in the shot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "それでもみんな、すぐ{user}さんだって\n分かっちゃったみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ everyone quickly figured out it was you.\nIt seems like everyone is paying close attention",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも{user}さんのこと\nよく見てるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to {user}-san.\nI've been asked questions like‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "撮影の時どんな感じだったの？　とかこの後、本当に\nデートしたんじゃない？　とか聞かれちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"What was it like during the shoot?\"\nand \"Did you really go on a date afterward?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、浮ついた空気になってるのか……\n女の子は本当にそういう話が好きなんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why the atmosphere is getting excited…\nGirls really like those kinds of stories‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "私もつい、{user}さんの手の繋ぎ方が\nすっごく優しくて素敵だったとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also accidentally mentioned how gentle and wonderful\nyour handholding was during the shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に歩く時も、私の歩幅に合わせてくれたとか\n話しちゃって……盛り上がっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And how you adjusted your pace to match mine when we walked together\nIt got everyone carried away while talking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……渚がさらに燃料を投下してる気がするんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It feels like Nagisa is adding fuel to the fire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、すみません、誤解されないよう\nみんなには後でちゃんと言っておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ I'm sorry. I'll make sure to clarify\nthings with everyone later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "頼むよ。俺はただの添え物なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please do. I'm just a prop‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！　相手が他の男性だったら\n手を繋ぐなんて絶対無理でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true! If it were anyone else‚ I would\nnever have been able to hold hands like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんだから\nあんな風にリラックス出来たんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because it's you‚ {user}-san‚\nthat I was able to relax like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。だからかな。撮影の時の渚\nいつもより大人びた顔だった。いい表情だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? That's probably why you had a more mature expression\nIt was a great look for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、渚が俺をからかって見せたけど\nそんな渚も意外だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you make fun of me that day‚ I was surprised too.\nYou were different from what I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれは……その、すみませんでした……\nあの日、寮に帰ってから、急に恥ずかしくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ that was… I'm sorry about that.\nAfter I returned to the dorm that day‚ I suddenly felt embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、あの時はすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really sorry for what happened then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、全然嫌な感じはしなかったよ\nそれどころか、渚の新しい魅力を発見出来た気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I didn't feel uncomfortable at all.\nIn fact‚ I think I discovered a new side of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　そ、そうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
