      "text": "ごめんごめん。さて、おーい、みんな\nお喋りはそろそろ切り上げて、撮影を再開しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. Well‚ hey everyone‚\nlet's wrap the chit-chat up and get back to shooting.",
        "id": ""
