        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、琴乃ちゃん。理想のクリスマスデートって\n言われた時、すぐにイメージは浮かんだんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ Kotono-chan. When I was asked about\nthe ideal Christmas date‚ I immediately had an image in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ？　楽しそうだから、やってみたかった？\nそ、そうだったんだ……ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Did you want to try it because it sounded fun?\nI see… I'm sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "――琴乃ちゃん、最近凄く忙しそうだったから……\nでも、そうだね。これからはちゃんと相談するね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Kotono-chan‚ you seemed really busy lately…\nBut you're right. I'll make sure to discuss it properly from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、急なお仕事が入って\nとっても困ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san had a sudden work assignment‚\nand it seemed an urgent business……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "私、どうしても助けてあげたくなったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just couldn't help but want to help…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　その気持ち、分かる？　ふふっ、だよね！\n{user}さんって、ほっとけないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? You understand that feeling? Hehe‚ I thought so!\nYou know {user}-san is someone I can't ignore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはどんなクリスマスデートが理想なの？\nよく分からない？　ふふっ私と遊園地に行きたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of Christmas date do Kotono-chan think would be ideal?\nYou're not sure? Hehe‚ you wanna go to an amusement park with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、そうだね。私も今はまだ\n琴乃ちゃんとデートするのが一番かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that sounds good. Right now‚\ngoing on a date with Kotono-chan might be the best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンぺスト新曲発売当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of releasing Moon Tempest's new song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1833.3333334000201,
          "startTime": 226.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 225.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます！\n{user}さん、新曲の評判どうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning!\n{user}-san‚ how's the reception of our new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。売り上げ、評判ともに上々だ\n早く生で聴きたいって話題になってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's doing really well. Both sales and reviews are great.\nPeople are talking about how they can't wait to hear it live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか！　良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? That's fantastic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それから評判といえば、渚の載った雑誌も好評だ\n渚の表情が、とても演技には見えないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of good reviews‚ the magazine featuring you is also receiving a lot of praise.\nThey say your expressions don't seem like acting at all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "色っぽいというか……小悪魔的だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and it's described as seductive‚ like a little devil.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs028.m4a",
      "text": "そんな！　私なんて普通ですよ\n小悪魔っていえば、ほら、こころちゃんとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way! I'm just an ordinary person.\nSpeaking of little devil‚ well‚ Kokoro-chan‚ for example…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "こころは少しあざといからな……\n素の渚は案外、こころより小悪魔なのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro can be more about being wicked……\nMaybe your natural self is more like little devil than Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs029.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　からかわないで下さい！\nあの時はちょっと調子に乗っちゃっただけなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez! Please don't tease me like that!\nI just got carried away that one time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs030.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私には琴乃ちゃんがいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I have Kotono-chan with me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs031.m4a",
      "text": "私の一番理想のクリスマスデートは\nやっぱり琴乃ちゃんとのデートです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so my ideal Christmas date is definitely\nwith Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9566.666666600042,
          "startTime": 295.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-ngs032.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今日はこれから琴乃ちゃんと\n待ち合わせなんです！　そろそろ失礼しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'm meeting up with Kotono-chan today!\nI have to go now. Excuse me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃とのデートが一番か……\n今はまだ、それでいいのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A date with Kotono is your top choice…\nMaybe‚ for now‚ that's the best choice.",
